This paper is primarily focused on face recognition using deep convolutional networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the properties of deep neural activations, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper evaluates its approach on benchmark datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
